overview: This DVD magazine features a digest of the solo corners and MC corners from the ANGERME 2018 Haru Live House "Juunin Toiro" in March 2018! There are tears, explosive laughter, and plenty of charm expected from the ten personalities in ANGERME! Rehearsal footage of the "CUPS" VTR shown during the hall tour in April is also included.  It was released on May 28, 2018 as merchandise for the ANGERME Concert Tour 2018 Haru Juunin Toiro + Final.
title: ANGERME DVD Magazine Vol.18
